        <div class="testimony-card d-flex align-content-center">
          <%= image_tag 'photographer-one.jpg', class: 'preview-avatar mb-2', width: '100px', height: '100px' %>
          <div class="ml-3 mt-3">
            <div class="d-flex flex-direction-column">
              <p>
                "I was surprised how effective HomeTog was with helping me find clients. This is the only way I book gigs now."
              </p>
            </div>
            <p class="d-flex flex-row-reverse testimony-author mb-5">
              -Edson Mclaren
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="testimony-card mt-3 d-flex">
          <%= image_tag 'girlavatar2.jpeg', class: 'preview-avatar mb-2', width: '100px', height: '100px' %>
          <div class="pl-3 mt-3">
            <div>
              <p>
                "I was in a panic trying to find a real estate photographer and HomeTog helped me find one last minute."
              </p>
            </div>
            <p class="d-flex flex-row-reverse testimony-author">
              -Jeda Demillio
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ml-3">
      <div class="testimony-content">
        <div class="testimony-card d-flex">
          <%= image_tag 'girlavatar1.jpeg', class: 'preview-avatar mb-2', width: '100px', height: '100px'  %>
          <div class="ml-3 mt-3">
            <div>
              <p>
                "I used to have to rely on word of mouth to find a real estate photgrapher, but not anymore."
              </p>
            </div>
            <p class="d-flex flex-row-reverse testimony-author mb-5">
